text:
Helen Hernandez (born 2000 in Oranjestad, Aruba) is a Aruban model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Aruba Universe 2020.
Early life.
Hernandez was born in Oranjestad, Aruba. She spoke in a dialect called Papiamento which is a mix of Spanish, Dutch, Portuguese, and English.
Miss Aruba 2020.
Hernandez joined Miss Aruba 2020, where she was crowned as Miss Aruba Universe 2020.
Miss Universe 2020.
As Miss Aruba, Hernandez will represent Aruba at Miss Universe 2020 pageant.
